Hi all I am experiencing some unknown issue with honeybee. After I updated the whole script manually I ran into a message "1. Solution exception:honeybee_ExtraConstrProps" In the report it says: Current document units is in Meters
Conversion to Meters will be applied = 1.000
[1 of 8] Writing simulation parameters...
Can't find ddy file next to the EPW.
Extreme values from the weather file design will be used instead.
[2 of 8] No context surfaces...
[3 of 8] Writing geometry...
[4 of 8] Writing Electric Load Center - Generator specifications ...
[5 of 8] Writing materials and constructions...
Runtime error (KeyNotFoundException): honeybee_ExtraConstrProps
Traceback:
line 2152, in main, "<string>"
line 2364, in script In order to solve it, I followed the topic below: [http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topic/show?id=2985...](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topic/show?id=2985220%3ATopic%3A1601436&xg_source=msg) In my case I only ran into further troubles with IDF file and some message about missing ControlProgram in Objects. I am uploading the gh file for you to see. PLS help me, I ran out of ideas.
